{
  "stem": "20575.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But while we were in Vienna, we spend all the time together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She came to my house, I went to her house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Went to the cemetery, working there, she was with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Always together, always together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then when she came to Terezin, we were in the same room, and always best friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when we went to Auschwitz-- I will tell you that later-- I met her there again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She lost everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Father, mother, sister, nephew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody went right the same day into the gas chamber, and by-- by, I don't know, miracle, she walked in in Auschwitz, when we were already in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother saw her, and says, Gertie, where are your-- she says, I'm all by myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So she says, come-- come here, stay here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't know we were standing in line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So from that time on, we were always together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Gertie Taussig, T-A-U-S-S-I-G.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now she's Gertie Meltzer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to live in Levittown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the reason that I moved here from Forrest Hills.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that I didn't have anybody else here, so we were always very close, and still are.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just by talking, just being there, just knowing that there's someone that from before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you made other, new friends, but this was something that goes way back, and it still goes way back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we still see each other, and we still go together to the opera, so we have kind of a-- it was like people think, most of the people think, we are sisters because she always said that we are sisters.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't want to start telling where are your parents, this one was killed, so we just said we're sisters.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
